lead_paragraph: The University of Wisconsin has cleared former basketball coach Bo Ryan of allegations that he had misused school resources while having an "improper personal relationship" with a woman, the school said.

headline.print_headline: Wisconsin Clears Retired Bo Ryan Over Affair Allegations
